				<td colspan="2"><span>Here is a link to Shass's guide listed in the Guides section:
<br />

<br />
<a target="_new" href=""></a>http://www.eqdiva.com/EQ/Guide.aspx?id=96&amp;ForumID=132<a target="_new" href=""></a>
<br />

<br />
Basically, you hit the forward (up), left <i>or</i> right arrows, and enter at the same time and release to go in an automatic circle.
<br />

<br />
Your circle size will vary by how fast you're running.</span></td>
